Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才刚见面就这么冲动呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃过一劫了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算上你们就是73794
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的生命将化为世界革命的基石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:28.82,IN_M_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seilien coffin airget-lamh tron
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化学武器工厂那边已经拜托绪川先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在追捕逃跑的管理者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚她们？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们在救援藤尧和友里时遭遇了炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.99,0:04:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事急从权　就让她们使用了最后的K型
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LiNKER…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可如果不是进行过针对性调整的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药效无法持续很长时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.67,0:04:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶快回去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋　我们这边就不是任务了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要信任同伴们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔博士在芯片里储存的LiNKER制造配方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来我的任务就是对其进行分析
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我迟迟没有完成才…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也同样信任着我们的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信任同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我们Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算来了啊 Symphogear
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于肯露面了啊　巴伐利亚光明会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又是在策划什么阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,革命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将人类历史引回正轨乃是吾等经年夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击没有效果Death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦　不要乱跑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来要用这个让她们老实一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连这身体都是卡萝尔给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来我都只是在拖大家后腿而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你们还真这么觉得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有效果？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是和NOISE一样有那个什么相位差吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那受到Symphogear攻击后不应该不产生调律啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说是有减伤的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就送它超越极限的一击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再生？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　这是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到的伤害都会彻底消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来实验是成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颠覆了本应是不可逆转的法则　超越常理的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术终于攀上了人类智慧的巅峰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令神之力降于现世
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三十六计走为上策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑不掉的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛　伤到脸蛋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面就是我们的村子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那帮大兵肯定会逃去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alca-NOISE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是敢搞什么小动作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙全都会被Alca-NOISE分解掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚说的就是我们计算出的撤退路线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这有多高吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直和蛇一样纠缠不清
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是大个头的破蛇Death
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时机已到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真烦死人Death
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(605,666.333)}Yohualtepoztli
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么不让夜之斧乘胜追击了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经确认了神之力的完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天小试身手就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是穷寇莫追咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个　加紧神祇的回收
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我走就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然会造成不必要的牺牲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯提芬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38}走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上　立花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
