Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯提芬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.30,0:10:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已拘捕工厂的管理者
